where &quot;q&quot;e is the elementary charge. The average net deflection by all the electrons within this arbitrary cylinder of effect around the alpha particle&#x27;s path is

formula_105

where &quot;N&quot;0 is the number of electrons per unit volume and formula_106 is the volume of this cylinder.

